# Secrets — never commit. ``~/.abyss/`` is the runtime data dir
# (VAPID keypair, push subscriptions, bot tokens). Guard against
# anyone accidentally creating an ``.abyss/`` inside the repo, and
# against stray PEM / key files landing anywhere in the tree.
.abyss/
**/.abyss/
*.pem
*.key
vapid-keys.json
push-subscriptions.json
.DS_Store
